logicalColumns.name: Calc GL Parent Product Line
logicalColumns.description:
Based On SLA (Sub Ledger Account) ccid (Segment 5) :

CASE  "SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment"  
   WHEN '400' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '410' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '430' then   'MB - SP'
   WHEN '470' then   'MB - Consumables'  
   WHEN '393' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '392' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '398' then   'Customer Support'  
   WHEN '394' then   'Customer Support'
ELSE

  CASE  LEFT("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment"  , 1)   
    WHEN  '1' THEN 'Systems'
    WHEN  '2' THEN 'FDM-Systems'
    WHEN  '5' THEN 'Consumables'
    WHEN  '6' THEN 'Consumables'
    WHEN  '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumables'
    WHEN  '8' THEN 'Customer Support'
    WHEN  '9' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP'
     ELSE   'Other'
  END
END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE %1 WHEN '400' THEN 'MB - Systems' WHEN '410' THEN 'MB - Systems' WHEN '430' THEN 'MB - SP' WHEN '470' THEN 'MB - Consumables' WHEN '393' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' WHEN '392' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' WHEN '398' THEN 'Customer Support' WHEN '394' THEN 'Customer Support' ELSE  CASE  LEFT(%1, 1) WHEN '1' THEN 'Systems' WHEN '2' THEN 'FDM-Systems' WHEN '5' THEN 'Consumables' WHEN '6' THEN 'Consumables' WHEN '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumables' WHEN '8' THEN 'Customer Support' WHEN '9' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' ELSE 'Other' END  END
expressionObjects: logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Invoice Distribution.Calc GL Product Line Segment

logicalColumns.name: Calc GL Product Line Family
logicalColumns.description:
Based On SLA (Sub Ledger Account)  (Segment 5) :

CASE  "SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment"  
   WHEN '890' then   'Service'
   WHEN '999' then   'FDM-Service'
   WHEN '400' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '410' then   'MB - Systems'
   WHEN '430' then   'MB - SP'
   WHEN '470' then   'MB - Consumables'  
   WHEN '393' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '392' then   'FDM-Maintenance and SP'  
   WHEN '398' then   'Customer Support'  
   WHEN '394' then   'Customer Support'

ELSE
   CASE WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 101 and 189 THEN 'Equipment'
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)    BETWEEN 191 AND 199 THEN 'Equipment Other'  
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 201 and 271 THEN 'FDM-Equipment'  
             WHEN CAST("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment" AS DOUBLE)  BETWEEN 272 and 299 THEN 'FDM-Equipment Other'  

   ELSE
      CASE  LEFT("SSYS"."Dim - Invoice Distribution"."Calc GL Product Line Segment"  , 1)   
         WHEN  '5' THEN 'Resins'
         WHEN  '6' THEN 'Resins'
         WHEN  '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumable'
         WHEN  '8' THEN 'Service'
         WHEN  '9' THEN 'FDM-Service'
         ELSE   'Other'
      END
   END
END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE %1 WHEN '890' THEN 'Service' WHEN '999' THEN 'FDM-Service' WHEN '400' THEN 'MB - Systems' WHEN '410' THEN 'MB - Systems' WHEN '430' THEN 'MB - SP' WHEN '470' THEN 'MB - Consumables' WHEN '393' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' WHEN '392' THEN 'FDM-Maintenance and SP' WHEN '398' THEN 'Customer Support' WHEN '394' THEN 'Customer Support' ELSE  CASE  WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 101 AND 189 THEN 'Equipment' WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 191 AND 199 THEN 'Equipment Other' WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 201 AND 271 THEN 'FDM-Equipment' WHEN  CAST (%1 AS DOUBLE PRECISION ) BETWEEN 272 AND 299 THEN 'FDM-Equipment Other' ELSE  CASE  LEFT(%1, 1) WHEN '5' THEN 'Resins' WHEN '6' THEN 'Resins' WHEN '7' THEN 'FDM-Consumable' WHEN '8' THEN 'Service' WHEN '9' THEN 'FDM-Service' ELSE 'Other' END  END  END
expressionObjects: logicalColumn:SSYS_SF.Dim - Invoice Distribution.Calc GL Product Line Segment
